en_251403_0	In order to evaluate the ongoing progress of the National Housing Development Authority (NHDA) - funded 9 houses, being built by 65 Division troops for low-income families in Thunukkai area, Major General Kumara Peiris, General Officer Commanding (GOC), 65 Division went to see them and meet potential beneficiaries.
en_251403_1	The GOC spoke to the beneficiaries and listened to them with a view to further making any improvements to the new houses if necessary before they are brought to completion.
en_251403_2	Those beneficiaries expressed their satisfaction over the manner the soldiers are carrying out construction work at the request of the NHDA.
